author: Warhammer
description:
Darktide's new class Hive Scum is coming December 2, 2025!

The Hive Scum comes screaming from the depths of the hive, leaving destruction and mayhem as they decimate their enemies from afar with dual-wielding pistols & explosives.
Up close they are equally lethal, fighting dirty and tearing through enemies with makeshift crowbars, saws and dual-wielded shivs. Their fighting prowess is further enhanced by Toxins and signature customizable Stimm.
